{"analytics_identifier":"OT1305","base_path":"/government/organisations/government-recruitment-service","content_id":"cd863c32-b26f-472a-b77a-f088dee7ba40","description":"The Government Recruitment Service (GRS) was launched in September 2017 and is part of the Cabinet Office’s Government People Group. GRS delivers award-winning recruitment services and functions for organisations across the Civil Service, supporting and enabling the recruitment of exceptional civil servants. GRS is part of the Government People Group .","details":{"acronym":"GRS","alternative_format_contact_email":"cshrcomms@cabinetoffice.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Government Recruitment Service (GRS) was launched in September 2017 and is part of the Cabinet Office’s Government People Group. GRS delivers award-winning recruitment services and functions for organisations across the Civil Service, supporting and enabling the recruitment of exceptional civil servants.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Government Recruitment Service\">GRS</abbr> is part of the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/government-people-group\">Government People Group</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"civil-service","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Government Recruitment Service"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/government-recruitment-service/about/complaints-procedure","title":"Complaints procedure"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"Blog post","href":"https://civilservice.blog.gov.uk/2024/11/18/four-steps-to-success-tips-for-candidates-applying-to-the-civil-service/","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/67d1688d830cc78f825c32c0/s712_Blog_post__960_x_640_px_.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/67d1688da6d78876a3fb0a0b/s465_Blog_post__960_x_640_px_.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/67d1